<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now we gotta start let's get move!!</i></b></font>

17
00:00:57,934 --> 00:00:59,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's move into the brand new world</i></b></font>

18
00:00:59,834 --> 00:01:02,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's dive into the brand new trip</i></b></font>

19
00:01:02,074 --> 00:01:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Frightened by the wide world</i></b></font>

20
00:01:05,844 --> 00:01:10,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We've just begun, now we go</i>
<i>full speed and funky beat</i></b></font>

21
00:01:10,114 --> 00:01:13,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We will shine around the world</i></b></font>

22
00:01:13,514 --> 00:01:16,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Trip to the world</i>
<i>Yo! Here we go unknown world</i></b></font>

23
00:01:16,284 --> 00:01:18,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We newborn travelers</i></b></font>

24
00:01:18,354 --> 00:01:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The unfamiliar walk is still charming</i></b></font>

25
00:01:20,554 --> 00:01:22,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The place you want to go is under your feet!</i></b></font>

26
00:01:22,424 --> 00:01:23,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So many people in this world</i></b></font>

27
00:01:23,764 --> 00:01:26,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's not as if there isn't</i>
<i>backstabbing once in a while</i></b></font>

28
00:01:26,194 --> 00:01:28,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's warp past these boring things</i></b></font>

29
00:01:28,034 --> 00:01:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And go straight to our reason for living</i></b></font>

30
00:01:29,534 --> 00:01:31,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's our law!</i></b></font>

31
00:01:54,454 --> 00:01:55,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was dangerous!</b></font>

32
00:01:55,894 --> 00:01:57,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What terrible driving...</b></font>

33
00:02:00,594 --> 00:02:02,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, you.</b></font>

34
00:02:02,164 --> 00:02:05,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hang in there. Are you all right?</b></font>

35
00:02:05,764 --> 00:02:09,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry, it's all my fault.</b></font>

36
00:02:09,274 --> 00:02:12,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry...</b></font>

37
00:02:12,344 --> 00:02:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hang on! I'll call an ambulance!</b></font>

38
00:02:18,014 --> 00:02:23,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 3: The Downhill Specialist Appears"</b></font>

39
00:02:24,054 --> 00:02:25,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

40
00:02:25,584 --> 00:02:27,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani got in an accident?</b></font>

41
00:02:27,754 --> 00:02:29,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When did it happen?</b></font>

42
00:02:29,054 --> 00:02:32,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Last night, he hit a guardrail
while coming down Akina.</b></font>

43
00:02:32,624 --> 00:02:33,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was he hurt?</b></font>

44
00:02:33,864 --> 00:02:35,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not too badly...</b></font>

45
00:02:35,564 --> 00:02:38,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's only minor whiplash...</b></font>

46
00:02:38,434 --> 00:02:41,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but he's really upset about the whole thing.</b></font>

47
00:02:41,374 --> 00:02:44,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard his car is pretty messed up.</b></font>

48
00:02:44,204 --> 00:02:47,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then what about the meet on Saturday?</b></font>

49
00:02:47,944 --> 00:02:50,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's hopeless...</b></font>

50
00:02:50,244 --> 00:02:53,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, we need to find
a substitute for Iketani.</b></font>

51
00:02:55,584 --> 00:03:02,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Automobiles"</b></font>

52
00:02:56,054 --> 00:02:58,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome.</b></font>

53
00:02:58,284 --> 00:02:59,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani?</b></font>

54
00:02:59,624 --> 00:03:01,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all right for you to go out?</b></font>

55
00:03:01,524 --> 00:03:04,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm okay. How's my car?</b></font>

56
00:03:04,394 --> 00:03:07,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's in the back garage, but we
still haven't done anything.</b></font>

57
00:03:07,834 --> 00:03:10,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We can't do anything until the parts arrive.</b></font>

58
00:03:42,234 --> 00:03:44,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

59
00:03:47,974 --> 00:03:51,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me. Fried tofu, please.</b></font>

60
00:03:51,544 --> 00:03:55,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes... I'm coming.</b></font>

61
00:03:55,244 --> 00:03:56,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got in an accident?</b></font>

62
00:03:56,984 --> 00:03:58,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

63
00:03:58,944 --> 00:04:02,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The meet is pretty soon. What will you do?</b></font>

64
00:04:02,314 --> 00:04:05,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I came to ask you a favor
about that, Mr. Fujiwara.</b></font>

65
00:04:05,554 --> 00:04:07,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--A favor?
--Yes.</b></font>

66
00:04:07,694 --> 00:04:09,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At the meet...</b></font>

67
00:04:09,224 --> 00:04:11,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...can you please drive in my place?</b></font>

68
00:04:13,594 --> 00:04:15,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I beg you, Mr. Fujiwara!</b></font>

69
00:04:15,594 --> 00:04:18,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch!</b></font>

70
00:04:18,404 --> 00:04:19,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My neck...!</b></font>

71
00:04:19,864 --> 00:04:21,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't die.</b></font>

72
00:04:21,604 --> 00:04:25,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Fujiwara, I'm sure you
know how a street racer feels.</b></font>

73
00:04:25,744 --> 00:04:28,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't let the local drivers lose.</b></font>

74
00:04:28,544 --> 00:04:32,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, even if an old guy
like me went out there,</b></font>

75
00:04:32,584 --> 00:04:34,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he would just be out of place.</b></font>

76
00:04:34,454 --> 00:04:37,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I grew up racing on Akina.</b></font>

77
00:04:37,784 --> 00:04:42,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those Akagi Red Suns obviously
are making fools of Akina's drivers.</b></font>

78
00:04:42,724 --> 00:04:44,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't stand it!</b></font>

79
00:04:44,424 --> 00:04:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to show them that Akina
has a street racer with true skill!</b></font>

80
00:04:49,594 --> 00:04:52,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Fujiwara, you are the one who can do it!</b></font>

81
00:04:52,404 --> 00:04:56,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have already defeated Akagi's
fastest, the Takahashi Brothers.</b></font>

82
00:04:57,744 --> 00:05:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I beg you, Mr. Fujiwara.</b></font>

83
00:05:02,044 --> 00:05:04,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"We accept credit cards"</b></font>

84
00:05:08,754 --> 00:05:11,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is this? We're already closed!</b></font>

85
00:05:11,984 --> 00:05:16,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

86
00:05:13,554 --> 00:05:16,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be rude. High octane, fill it up.</b></font>

87
00:05:16,854 --> 00:05:20,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How cheeky. You want me to put
high octane in that Eight-Six?</b></font>

88
00:05:22,734 --> 00:05:24,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must have been you, Yuichi.</b></font>

89
00:05:24,534 --> 00:05:28,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You told the weird rumor to that kid, Iketani.</b></font>

90
00:05:28,204 --> 00:05:31,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure. It wasn't a lie either.</b></font>

91
00:05:31,704 --> 00:05:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what about it?</b></font>

92
00:05:33,344 --> 00:05:34,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He came again today,</b></font>

93
00:05:34,674 --> 00:05:37,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with a bandage on his head and a neck brace.</b></font>

94
00:05:37,244 --> 00:05:40,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He asked me to drive in his place.</b></font>

95
00:05:40,014 --> 00:05:43,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I can't say that I hate that kind of guy.</b></font>

96
00:05:43,014 --> 00:05:46,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't hate him,
then why don't you do it?</b></font>

97
00:05:46,724 --> 00:05:49,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani is a good guy.</b></font>

98
00:05:49,094 --> 00:05:50,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, thanks.</b></font>

99
00:05:50,564 --> 00:05:53,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want to go sticking my
nose into these kiddie fights.</b></font>

100
00:05:53,864 --> 00:05:56,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not my style.</b></font>

101
00:05:56,464 --> 00:06:01,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So then it's all right if a kid
shows up at a kiddie fight, right?</b></font>

102
00:06:01,334 --> 00:06:03,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you talking about Takumi?</b></font>

103
00:06:03,234 --> 00:06:04,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right.</b></font>

104
00:06:04,574 --> 00:06:07,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's gotten pretty good, right?</b></font>

105
00:06:07,674 --> 00:06:09,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He still has a ways to go...</b></font>

106
00:06:09,644 --> 00:06:14,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it's Akina's downhill,
he wouldn't lose to anybody.</b></font>

107
00:06:14,184 --> 00:06:16,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, except me, of course.</b></font>

108
00:06:16,514 --> 00:06:18,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your competitive spirit is showing.</b></font>

109
00:06:18,724 --> 00:06:22,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder where he got his
stubborn nature from...</b></font>

110
00:06:22,054 --> 00:06:26,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But even if I order him to go race,
that won't make him want to.</b></font>

111
00:06:26,064 --> 00:06:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, because of those
bandages on Iketani's head,</b></font>

112
00:06:30,034 --> 00:06:32,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll try to think of a good strategy.</b></font>

113
00:06:47,884 --> 00:06:50,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A promise should never be broken.</b></font>

114
00:06:50,854 --> 00:06:53,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are only two kinds of people that I hate.</b></font>

115
00:06:53,024 --> 00:06:55,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>People who break their promises
and people who smoke.</b></font>

116
00:06:55,854 --> 00:06:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to use the car this Sunday.</b></font>

117
00:06:59,594 --> 00:07:01,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sunday... you can't.</b></font>

118
00:07:01,994 --> 00:07:03,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why not?</b></font>

119
00:07:03,494 --> 00:07:06,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take care of the morning delivery.</b></font>

120
00:07:06,064 --> 00:07:07,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not the problem.</b></font>

121
00:07:07,834 --> 00:07:11,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to use it to go to
a town meeting on Sunday.</b></font>

122
00:07:11,574 --> 00:07:14,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? This is bad...</b></font>

123
00:07:14,674 --> 00:07:18,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really need the car on Sunday.</b></font>

124
00:07:19,744 --> 00:07:22,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be a girl.</b></font>

125
00:07:22,854 --> 00:07:24,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>None of your business.</b></font>

126
00:07:24,424 --> 00:07:26,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Quit being so stubborn. Just let me use it.</b></font>

127
00:07:26,854 --> 00:07:29,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just a crappy old car...</b></font>

128
00:07:29,194 --> 00:07:31,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take it if I want to.</b></font>

129
00:07:31,064 --> 00:07:33,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A car won't move without a key.</b></font>

130
00:07:33,524 --> 00:07:36,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll put it on a string and
wear it around my neck.</b></font>

131
00:07:36,194 --> 00:07:38,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not fair!</b></font>

132
00:07:38,334 --> 00:07:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you really want it that bad,
I'll think about it.</b></font>

133
00:07:42,234 --> 00:07:43,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

134
00:07:43,374 --> 00:07:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But there is a condition.</b></font>

135
00:07:45,544 --> 00:07:47,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Condition?</b></font>

136
00:07:47,214 --> 00:07:50,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Saturday night, go meet some brat
who's known as the fastest on Akagi</b></font>

137
00:07:50,214 --> 00:07:52,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and beat the pants off him</b></font>

138
00:07:52,384 --> 00:07:54,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>on Mt. Akina's downhill.</b></font>

139
00:07:54,384 --> 00:07:57,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

140
00:07:57,054 --> 00:07:59,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you do that, you can use
the car with no conditions,</b></font>

141
00:07:59,724 --> 00:08:03,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and you'll get a full tank of gas.</b></font>

142
00:08:03,124 --> 00:08:05,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Full tank of gas?</b></font>

143
00:08:07,534 --> 00:08:09,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Full tank of gas...</i></b></font>

144
00:08:09,394 --> 00:08:12,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This offer is truly irresistible.</i></b></font>

145
00:08:12,164 --> 00:08:14,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm out of money, too.</i></b></font>

146
00:08:14,734 --> 00:08:17,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What're you going to do?</b></font>

147
00:08:17,034 --> 00:08:19,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, let me think a minute.</b></font>

148
00:08:21,574 --> 00:08:24,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, take all the time you need.</b></font>

149
00:08:26,484 --> 00:08:28,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Takahashi"</b></font>

150
00:08:42,694 --> 00:08:45,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm coming in.</b></font>

151
00:08:45,164 --> 00:08:47,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, good timing.</b></font>

152
00:08:47,734 --> 00:08:50,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanted to ask you something.</b></font>

153
00:08:50,204 --> 00:08:52,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it, brother?</b></font>

154
00:08:52,204 --> 00:08:54,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six that you saw on Akina...</b></font>

155
00:08:54,914 --> 00:08:57,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you describe the speed of the car,</b></font>

156
00:08:57,044 --> 00:08:59,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>theoretically speaking?</b></font>

157
00:08:59,214 --> 00:09:01,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, gimme a break.</b></font>

158
00:09:01,814 --> 00:09:05,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlike you, I'm not good at that kind of stuff.</b></font>

159
00:09:05,184 --> 00:09:06,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I always say,</b></font>

160
00:09:06,824 --> 00:09:09,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the most important part
of driving technique is here.</b></font>

161
00:09:09,994 --> 00:09:11,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whenever you battle somebody,</b></font>

162
00:09:11,524 --> 00:09:15,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can stay behind them and
learn whatever you want to know.</b></font>

163
00:09:15,134 --> 00:09:17,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From your opponent's habits and weaknesses</b></font>

164
00:09:17,504 --> 00:09:19,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to how well their suspension is set up.</b></font>

165
00:09:19,904 --> 00:09:24,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your ability to analyze is almost scary.</b></font>

166
00:09:24,404 --> 00:09:27,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In my opinion, the fact that
you can drive without thinking</b></font>

167
00:09:27,374 --> 00:09:29,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and still keep up with me</b></font>

168
00:09:29,044 --> 00:09:31,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>means that you're the one who's truly scary.</b></font>

169
00:09:31,514 --> 00:09:33,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you could apply theories to your skill,</b></font>

170
00:09:33,714 --> 00:09:35,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you'd be the ideal driver.</b></font>

171
00:09:35,854 --> 00:09:39,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I lost because I didn't know
the road and I was careless.</b></font>

172
00:09:39,924 --> 00:09:42,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never been disgraced like this before.</b></font>

173
00:09:42,824 --> 00:09:45,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The inside of that Eight-Six must be a monster.</b></font>

174
00:09:45,924 --> 00:09:48,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A monster, you say?</b></font>

175
00:09:48,034 --> 00:09:50,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is getting more interesting...</b></font>

176
00:09:52,434 --> 00:09:55,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tomorrow is the meet.
Maybe I should go and watch.</b></font>

177
00:10:04,044 --> 00:10:06,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

178
00:10:06,944 --> 00:10:10,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Saturday has arrived!</b></font>

179
00:10:10,214 --> 00:10:11,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What about it?</b></font>

180
00:10:13,124 --> 00:10:15,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean,
"What about it?"Today is the meet!</b></font>

181
00:10:15,554 --> 00:10:18,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The meet with the Akagi Red Suns!</b></font>

182
00:10:18,264 --> 00:10:22,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You promised that you'd borrow the
Eight-Six and we'd go watch, right?</b></font>

183
00:10:22,534 --> 00:10:25,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure. Speaking of which...</b></font>

184
00:10:25,234 --> 00:10:28,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is getting a bit complicated.</b></font>

185
00:10:28,404 --> 00:10:30,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did you say?</b></font>

186
00:10:30,304 --> 00:10:34,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd better not be trying to tell me
that you don't have the time...</b></font>

187
00:10:34,714 --> 00:10:37,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, that's not the reason...</b></font>

188
00:10:37,784 --> 00:10:39,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you back out at the last minute,</b></font>

189
00:10:39,244 --> 00:10:41,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you can kiss our friendship goodbye.</b></font>

190
00:10:41,914 --> 00:10:46,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Every day I've counted the days
on my fingers, waiting for today.</b></font>

191
00:10:46,984 --> 00:10:48,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know.</b></font>

192
00:10:48,794 --> 00:10:50,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Excuse me!</b></font>

193
00:10:50,794 --> 00:10:52,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fried tofu, please.</b></font>

194
00:10:52,794 --> 00:10:55,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, it's you again.</b></font>

195
00:10:55,164 --> 00:10:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't give up, do you...</b></font>

196
00:10:57,294 --> 00:10:59,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Fujiwara, I beg you.</b></font>

197
00:10:59,564 --> 00:11:01,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At today's meet...</b></font>

198
00:11:02,604 --> 00:11:05,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I might do it...</b></font>

199
00:11:07,744 --> 00:11:11,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I might do it, that's what I said.</b></font>

200
00:11:11,184 --> 00:11:13,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On Akina tonight...</b></font>

201
00:11:13,584 --> 00:11:15,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Honestly?!</b></font>

202
00:11:15,954 --> 00:11:18,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ouch... My neck...</b></font>

203
00:11:18,624 --> 00:11:21,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, are you okay?</b></font>

204
00:11:21,024 --> 00:11:23,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you really going to come?</b></font>

205
00:11:23,294 --> 00:11:26,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't say for certain, but...</b></font>

206
00:11:26,094 --> 00:11:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I would say there's about a 50/50 chance.</b></font>

207
00:11:29,564 --> 00:11:31,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What time does it start?</b></font>

208
00:11:31,204 --> 00:11:33,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The gathering begins at eight o'clock,</b></font>

209
00:11:33,634 --> 00:11:35,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but the time attack begins at ten.</b></font>

210
00:11:35,634 --> 00:11:38,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ten o'clock...</b></font>

211
00:11:38,404 --> 00:11:42,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If an Eight-Six hasn't shown up
by ten, you can give up on waiting.</b></font>

212
00:11:42,914 --> 00:11:45,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll have to do it on your own.</b></font>

213
00:11:45,484 --> 00:11:47,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be waiting, Mr. Fujiwara.</b></font>

214
00:11:47,654 --> 00:11:50,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have faith that you'll definitely come.</b></font>

215
00:11:50,314 --> 00:11:53,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not definite. I said it's 50%.</b></font>

216
00:11:53,484 --> 00:11:56,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, you've already decided to come.</b></font>

217
00:11:56,724 --> 00:11:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our team will be waiting for you!</b></font>

218
00:11:59,594 --> 00:12:01,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, then, Mr. Fujiwara...</b></font>

219
00:12:01,194 --> 00:12:04,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll be waiting for you on
the top of Akina at 10 o'clock.</b></font>

220
00:12:17,684 --> 00:12:21,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just can't be cold to an eager guy like him.</i></b></font>

221
00:12:21,454 --> 00:12:24,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If Takumi won't do it, then should I go?</i></b></font>

222
00:12:26,054 --> 00:12:29,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No, no, I shouldn't. I'm getting excited.</i></b></font>

223
00:12:51,814 --> 00:12:54,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did something fun happen?</b></font>

224
00:12:54,984 --> 00:12:57,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem different today.</b></font>

225
00:12:57,214 --> 00:12:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

226
00:12:58,924 --> 00:13:01,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aren't I always like this?</b></font>

227
00:13:01,494 --> 00:13:04,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You look happy about something.</b></font>

228
00:13:04,764 --> 00:13:07,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actually, I'm going to the ocean
with my friend tomorrow.</b></font>

229
00:13:07,894 --> 00:13:09,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really excited about it!</b></font>

230
00:13:09,764 --> 00:13:12,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Friend? You mean a boy?</b></font>

231
00:13:12,264 --> 00:13:16,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? Of course not! I'm going with a girl!</b></font>

232
00:13:16,604 --> 00:13:19,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. Well, let's go to the department store,</b></font>

233
00:13:19,344 --> 00:13:22,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and I'll buy you a new bathing suit.</b></font>

234
00:13:22,514 --> 00:13:24,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's okay. I already bought one on my own.</b></font>

235
00:13:24,944 --> 00:13:27,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't need two of them.</b></font>

236
00:13:27,084 --> 00:13:30,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to see you in your bathing suit.</b></font>

237
00:13:30,184 --> 00:13:32,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's funny!</b></font>

238
00:13:32,054 --> 00:13:34,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've already seen everything.</b></font>

239
00:13:34,024 --> 00:13:35,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're such a perv, Papa!</b></font>

240
00:13:37,194 --> 00:13:39,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if tomorrow will be sunny.</b></font>

241
00:13:39,024 --> 00:13:41,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't ask me such a stupid thing.</b></font>

242
00:13:41,534 --> 00:13:44,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The weather is great all over Japan.</b></font>

243
00:13:44,564 --> 00:13:46,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you going somewhere?</b></font>

244
00:13:46,134 --> 00:13:48,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to the ocean.</b></font>

245
00:13:48,634 --> 00:13:50,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ocean?</b></font>

246
00:13:50,034 --> 00:13:51,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

247
00:13:51,704 --> 00:13:55,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm jealous! I want to go to the ocean, too!</b></font>

248
00:13:55,744 --> 00:13:57,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could it be...?</b></font>

249
00:13:57,044 --> 00:14:00,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're going with a girl?! A girl?!</b></font>

250
00:14:00,314 --> 00:14:01,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sort of...</b></font>

251
00:14:01,654 --> 00:14:04,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is it? Do I know her?</b></font>

252
00:14:04,154 --> 00:14:07,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is she cute? Does she have big ones?</b></font>

253
00:14:07,254 --> 00:14:09,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's very cute.</b></font>

254
00:14:10,754 --> 00:14:13,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Natsuki... Mogi...?</b></font>

255
00:14:13,924 --> 00:14:15,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

256
00:14:15,334 --> 00:14:18,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's cruel of you not to tell me.</b></font>

257
00:14:18,064 --> 00:14:22,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, but the situation didn't
give me a chance to invite you.</b></font>

258
00:14:22,334 --> 00:14:25,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Next time, okay?</b></font>

259
00:14:25,004 --> 00:14:26,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't cry.</b></font>

260
00:14:29,674 --> 00:14:32,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going to happen at today's battle?</b></font>

261
00:14:32,684 --> 00:14:37,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard that the Red Suns have
won every battle they've been in.</b></font>

262
00:14:37,384 --> 00:14:39,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The outcome is already obvious.</b></font>

263
00:14:39,624 --> 00:14:42,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina will be totally defeated.</b></font>

264
00:14:42,094 --> 00:14:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>However, the fastest team in
Gunma is not the Red Suns...</b></font>

265
00:14:45,064 --> 00:14:47,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's us, the Myogi Night Kids.</b></font>

266
00:14:47,694 --> 00:14:49,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takeshi, it's about time.</b></font>

267
00:14:49,534 --> 00:14:51,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, let's go.</b></font>

268
00:14:55,134 --> 00:14:58,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Born with only the purpose of running fast...</i></b></font>

269
00:14:58,044 --> 00:15:01,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A pure thoroughbred... the R32.</i></b></font>

270
00:15:01,474 --> 00:15:04,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It won't lose to Akagi's dumb rotaries.</i></b></font>

271
00:15:11,724 --> 00:15:13,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing.</i></b></font>

272
00:15:13,224 --> 00:15:16,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The mountain is lit up like a festival.</i></b></font>

273
00:15:16,824 --> 00:15:18,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rumors about this battle</i>
<i>between Iketani's team</i></b></font>

274
00:15:18,994 --> 00:15:22,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>and Akagi's fastest team</i></b></font>

275
00:15:22,334 --> 00:15:25,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>have spread all over the place.</i></b></font>

276
00:15:30,574 --> 00:15:32,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Which side will win?</i></b></font>

277
00:15:32,504 --> 00:15:35,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi's Eight-Six is Bunta's Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

278
00:15:35,714 --> 00:15:38,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It can't lose.</i></b></font>

279
00:15:38,414 --> 00:15:41,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's been a while since I've gotten this excited.</i></b></font>

280
00:15:51,194 --> 00:15:53,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, so many people!</b></font>

281
00:15:53,524 --> 00:15:57,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never seen such a huge crowd on Akina.</b></font>

282
00:15:57,134 --> 00:16:01,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Red Suns brought them all
here to show off their speed.</b></font>

283
00:16:01,634 --> 00:16:05,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we lose tonight, we'll be humiliated.</b></font>

284
00:16:05,144 --> 00:16:08,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By the way, the Eight-Six that
you were telling us about...</b></font>

285
00:16:08,144 --> 00:16:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it for real, Iketani?</b></font>

286
00:16:10,014 --> 00:16:11,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

287
00:16:11,584 --> 00:16:15,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't have any faith in that Eight-Six.</b></font>

288
00:16:15,684 --> 00:16:17,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard that Keisuke Takahashi's FD3S</b></font>

289
00:16:17,854 --> 00:16:20,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is lightly tuned for mountain driving.</b></font>

290
00:16:20,224 --> 00:16:24,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But even still, there is a rumor
that it's putting out over 350 HP.</b></font>

291
00:16:24,054 --> 00:16:26,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The difference in power is too great.</b></font>

292
00:16:26,364 --> 00:16:30,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even on the downhill, there's
no way an Eight-Six can compete!</b></font>

293
00:16:30,264 --> 00:16:34,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani, are you sure you
didn't hit your head too hard?</b></font>

294
00:16:34,734 --> 00:16:36,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six is an Eight-Six,</b></font>

295
00:16:36,534 --> 00:16:38,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but this is not a normal Eight-Six.</b></font>

296
00:16:38,374 --> 00:16:40,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke Takahashi said it himself...</b></font>

297
00:16:40,374 --> 00:16:42,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the outside, it's a normal panda Trueno,</b></font>

298
00:16:42,844 --> 00:16:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but inside, it's a monster machine.</b></font>

299
00:16:46,384 --> 00:16:47,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Trust me.</b></font>

300
00:16:47,854 --> 00:16:50,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he will come.</b></font>

301
00:16:54,184 --> 00:16:56,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he doesn't come...?</b></font>

302
00:16:56,354 --> 00:16:58,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is a huge crowd here.</b></font>

303
00:16:58,964 --> 00:17:02,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't want them to say
the Speed Stars ran away.</b></font>

304
00:17:02,494 --> 00:17:03,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he doesn't come...</b></font>

305
00:17:03,964 --> 00:17:06,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he doesn't come...?</b></font>

306
00:17:06,704 --> 00:17:11,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenji, represent our team and drive like hell!</b></font>

307
00:17:11,374 --> 00:17:14,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must be joking.</b></font>

308
00:17:18,344 --> 00:17:20,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A bunch of cars are coming.</b></font>

309
00:17:20,084 --> 00:17:22,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can hear the rotaries.</b></font>

310
00:17:27,354 --> 00:17:29,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Red Suns!</b></font>

