323
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:31,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not my friend anymore!</b></font>

324
00:18:31,854 --> 00:18:33,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That hurt!</b></font>

325
00:18:33,554 --> 00:18:37,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't wait anymore!
I'll have to go on my scooter.</b></font>

326
00:18:37,354 --> 00:18:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's begin the time attack at 10 o'clock,</b></font>

327
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:40,864
