328
00:18:40,864 --> 00:18:45,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It should be easier since it's late
and there aren't many other cars.</b></font>

329
00:18:45,704 --> 00:18:48,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll use radios at the start and finish points</b></font>

330
00:18:48,204 --> 00:18:49,874
