332
00:18:52,904 --> 00:18:55,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>officials will be placed at the blind corners,</b></font>

333
00:18:55,744 --> 00:18:57,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and in the event of oncoming traffic,</b></font>

334
00:18:57,714 --> 00:19:00,414
