335
00:19:00,414 --> 00:19:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see.</b></font>

336
00:19:01,714 --> 00:19:03,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seems like they've done this a lot.</b></font>

337
00:19:03,984 --> 00:19:07,524
