344
00:19:40,924 --> 00:19:43,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it? Starting to feel like going?</b></font>

345
00:19:43,694 --> 00:19:46,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure, but I don't really want to.</b></font>

346
00:19:46,424 --> 00:19:48,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why not? You've got no
confidence that you'll win?</b></font>

347
00:19:48,734 --> 00:19:51,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Drive like you normally drive,
