348
00:20:00,874 --> 00:20:02,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's here!</b></font>

349
00:20:02,244 --> 00:20:05,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's FD3S!</b></font>

350
00:20:16,524 --> 00:20:19,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible! Such a fast entry speed!</b></font>

351
00:20:20,794 --> 00:20:23,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Next is Ryosuke Takahashi!</b></font>

352
00:20:26,604 --> 00:20:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Run! Look out!</b></font>

353
00:20:38,984 --> 00:20:41,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's Ryosuke Takahashi for you.</b></font>

354
00:20:41,084 --> 00:20:43,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His skill is the real thing.</b></font>

355
00:20:53,994 --> 00:20:57,164
