366
00:21:39,704 --> 00:21:41,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Green Shopping Street"</b></font>

367
00:21:53,224 --> 00:21:55,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do I need a paper cup today?</b></font>

368
00:21:55,424 --> 00:21:59,924
