371
00:22:06,334 --> 00:22:08,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know, I know.</b></font>

372
00:22:08,404 --> 00:22:10,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I'm going.</b></font>

373
00:22:10,034 --> 00:22:11,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

374
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

375
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
