<i>--Give me that!</i></b></font>

407
00:24:32,444 --> 00:24:35,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hurry up and show yourself, Ghost of Akina!</i></b></font>

408
00:24:35,184 --> 00:24:37,714
